iHeartRadio,is,a,platform,for,searching,for,and,playing,live,radio,stations,and,shows,from,both,traditional,radio,stations,and,digital,radio,stations,Users,can,search,for,stations,and,shows,by,station,songs,and,music,artists,The,iHeartRadio,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,data,and,functionality,of,iHeartRadio,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Full,documentation,is,available,with,registration,and,login